WEBVTT

00:00:28.935 --> 00:00:31.020
ohangiga qaraganda

00:00:31.020 --> 00:00:33.648
bular kompliment.

00:00:33.648 --> 00:00:35.260
Lekin aynan shu iboralar, boshqa

00:00:35.260 --> 00:00:37.820
tomondan haqoratli va zaharhanda 
bo'lishi mumkin.

00:00:37.820 --> 00:00:40.906
Ohangda oddiy ifodaviy o'zgarishlar

00:00:40.906 --> 00:00:44.995
bizni aynan og'zaki kinoyaga olib 
kelishi mumkin.

00:00:44.995 --> 00:00:48.570
Va kimdir "ajoyib ob-havo!" deganida,

00:00:48.570 --> 00:00:52.126
inson rostan ham aynan yaxshi ob-havoni 
nazarda tutishi mumkin.

00:00:52.126 --> 00:00:53.259
Agar quyosh charaqlab,

00:00:53.259 --> 00:00:54.625
qushlar sayrayotgan

00:00:54.625 --> 00:00:56.611
va deyarli shamol yo'q bo'lsa.

00:00:56.611 --> 00:00:58.043
Agar ob-havo yomon bo'lsa,

00:00:58.043 --> 00:00:59.074
bulutlar yaqinlasha-

00:00:59.074 --> 00:01:01.178
yotgan va bo'ron boshlanayotgan bo'lsa,